						"description": "Ask a question about an uploaded book.\\n\\n🚨 RATE LIMIT FIX (429 RESOURCE_EXHAUSTED):\\nGemini free tier limits for gemini-2.0-flash:\\n  - Requests per minute: 15\\n  - Requests per day: 1500 (can exhaust quickly)\\n\\nFix options:\\n1. Wait 38s for per-minute reset, or midnight PT for daily reset\\n2. Add retry logic with 40s delay on 429 errors\\n3. Switch to 'gemini-1.5-flash' (higher free quota)\\n\\nRetry pattern:\\n  async function withRetry(fn, retries=3, delayMs=40000) {\\n    for (let i = 0; i < retries; i++) {\\n      try { return await fn(); }\\n      catch (err) {\\n        if (err.message?.includes('429') && i < retries-1)\\n          await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, delayMs));\\n        else throw err;\\n      }\\n    }\\n  }"
